      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Commercial CFD solver with documented QA procedures and regression test suite sufficient for MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 used under institutional software QA protocol. Vendor regression test suite covers turbulent rotating-frame flows. Version-controlled case files archived in institutional repository. Achieved level 2 exceeds MRL 2 requirement of level 1."
