      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not separately required at MRL 2; input uncertainty addressed through boundary condition documentation.",
      "rationale": "Blood viscosity (0.0035 Pa·s), density (1060 kg/m³), and hemolysis model constants drawn from published literature. Sensitivity of NIH to ±10% variation in viscosity assessed informally and found to produce less than 3% change in predicted NIH. Formal input uncertainty propagation not required at MRL 2."
